      "review_summary": "Adds iMessage outbound allowlist enforcement for normal sends, private API actions, and reply delivery, threads trusted requester sender context through shared outbound contexts, and adds focused regression tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +322, Tests +918. Total +1240 across 15 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source: current main reaches the iMessage send path without an outbound allowlist assertion, while the PR adds fail-closed checks before transport calls. I did not run a live iMessage reproduction.",
